## Taco Ipsum

Every day is taco ipsum tuesday. Um, Tabasco? No thanks, do you have any Cholula? I think I’ve overdosed on tacos. Yeah, apparently the taco shack was robbed. They left the money but took the tacos. Fish tacos with cabbage slaw and a side of chips and guac. CARNE ASADA!! It’s taco Tuesday Monday. Fish tacos: lettuce or cabbage, pico de gallo, avocado and a sour cream or citrus/mayonnaise sauce, all placed on top of a corn or flour tortilla. TACOS!! Ooh, with diced onions and a pinch of cilantro.
